titles.title: To designate the historic Federal Building located at 100 North Palafox Street in Pensacola, Florida, as the "Winston E. Arnow Federal Building".

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Transportation and Infrastructure.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Economic Development, Public Buildings and Emergency Management.

bill.summary:
4/1/2008--Introduced.
Designates the historic federal building located at 100 North Palafox Street in Pensacola, Florida, as the "Winston E. Arnow Federal Building."
